    <item>
      <title>A quick poem</title>
      <link>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2010/09/15/quick-poem/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Sep 2010 22:35:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2010/09/15/quick-poem/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Really quick now:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I was chatting to my friend over the email communicator and I typed out this poem whilst sitting on the tube. Looking
back I think it is kinda cool.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Oddly shaped electrical thing,&lt;br&gt;
With all the wires &amp;rsquo;n cables you bring.&lt;br&gt;
You&amp;rsquo;re my magnificent window to a world unseen,&lt;br&gt;
From robots and stars to mars&amp;rsquo; moon beams.&lt;br&gt;
Ever I ponder I will turn to you.&lt;br&gt;
Ever I ponder you show me what&amp;rsquo;s true.&lt;br&gt;
For you are the one that connects my life,&lt;br&gt;
Across oceans and seas to the people I like.&lt;br&gt;
I know not what I&amp;rsquo;ll do should this come to an end,&lt;br&gt;
You&amp;rsquo;re my oddly shaped electrical friend.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hope you like it!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure &gt;
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    
    &lt;img 
      
      srcset=&#39;
      
        /blog/2010/09/15/quick-poem/science_hu3f493b5bf5a99dc07835e70c3a7c3c75_454053_500x0_resize_q75_box.jpg 1x
      
      
